Definition: reflex erection of hairs of the skin in response to cold or emotional stress or skin irritation
Synonyms: gooseflesh, goose_bump, goosebump, goose_pimple, goose_skin, horripilation, verb, perception, horripilate, reflex, erection, of, hairs, the, skin, in, response, to, cold, or, emotional, stress, irritation
Category: noun.act
